<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Privacy Policy - <%= siteName %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <!-- SEO -->
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy of <%= siteName %>. Learn how we collect, use and protect your information. 18+ Adult Website.">
    
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="keywords" content="<%= keywords %>" />
    <link rel="icon" href="<%= img %>"/>
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= url %>/privacy">

    
    <!-- og tag -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Privacy Policy - <%= siteName %>">
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= url %>/privacy">
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= img %>">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Privacy Policy of <%= siteName %>. Learn how we collect, use and protect your information. 18+ Adult Website." />
    
    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Privacy Policy - <%= siteName %>">
    <meta name="twitter:site" content="@<%= url %>/privacy">
    <meta name="twitter:description"  content="Privacy Policy of <%= siteName %>. Learn how we collect, use and protect your information. 18+ Adult Website.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= img %>">
    <meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="Privacy Policy - <%= siteName %>">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    

    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #f1f1f1;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #111;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 { color: #ff0000; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        h2 { color: #ff4d4d; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 10px; }

        ul { margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; }

        a { color: #ff0000; text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: #ff4d4d; }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<%- include('header') %>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card">

        <h1>Privacy and Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> <%= lastUpdated %></p>

        <p>
            This Privacy Policy explains how <strong><%= siteName %></strong>
            ("Website", "we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and protects
            your information when you access our adult content platform.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Age Restriction</h2>
        <p>
            This website is strictly intended for users aged 18 years or older.
            We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors.
            If you believe a minor has provided us with information,
            please contact us immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>IP address and browser type</li>
            <li>Device information</li>
            <li>Pages visited and usage activity</li>
            <li>Cookies and tracking technologies</li>
            <li>Email address (if you contact us)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To operate and maintain the website</li>
            <li>To improve user experience</li>
            <li>To prevent fraud and illegal activity</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Cookies Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance
            your browsing experience, analyze traffic, and remember preferences.
            You can disable cookies through your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
            We may use third-party services such as analytics providers,
            hosting services, or advertising networks.
            These third parties may collect information in accordance with their own policies.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
            We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data.
            However, no online platform can guarantee complete security.
        </p>

        <h2>7. International Users</h2>
        <p>
            Our website is accessible worldwide.
            By using this platform, you consent to data processing
            in accordance with applicable international laws.
            The website is operated from Bangladesh.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>You may request access to your personal data.</li>
            <li>You may request correction or deletion where applicable.</li>
            <li>You may withdraw consent where legally permitted.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time.
            Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of changes.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy:
        </p>

        <p>
            Website: <a href="<%= siteDomain %>"><%= siteDomain %></a><br>
            Email: <a href="mailto:<%= email %>"><%= email %></a>
        </p>

    </div>
</div>

<%- include('footer') %>

</body>
</html>